Hadith on Sins: Major sins are idolatry, infanticide, adultery","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas'ud reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is the greatest sin?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cTo set up a partner alongside Allah, even though He alone created you.\u201d I said, \u201cWhat is next?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cTo kill your child, fearing\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32182,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/15\/avoid-seven-mortal-sins\/","url_meta":{"origin":32325,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Sins: Avoid seven major sins, idolatry, killing","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 15, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cStay away from seven mortal sins.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are they?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cIdolatry with Allah, occult magic, killing a soul that Allah has sanctified except for a just cause, consuming usury, usurping\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42699,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2025\/03\/07\/despair-major-sin\/","url_meta":{"origin":32325,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Kaba\u2019ir: Despairing of Allah\u2019s mercy a major sin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 7, 202